"title": "5608: warfare, strategies in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5608",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture describes the strategies employed by Israel in warfare. Although recognising the importance of military preparation, Scripture stresses that Israel's trust is to be in God, rather than military might or prowess.</p>\n<h2>Preparations for warfare</h2>\n<h3>Holding a council of war</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:18\">PRO 20:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:14\">PRO 11:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:6\">PRO 24:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:31-Luke14:32\">LUK 14:31–14:32</a></p>\n<h3>Assembling an army</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:1\">2SA 18:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num1:2-Num1:3\">NUM 1:2–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:6-1Sam11:8\">1SA 11:6–11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:5-2Chr25:6\">2CH 25:5–25:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:11-2Chr26:14\">2CH 26:11–26:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:10-Dan11:13\">DAN 11:10–11:13</a></p>\n<h3>Reconnaissance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:32\">NUM 21:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:22\">DEU 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:1\">JOS 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:2-Josh7:3\">JOS 7:2–7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:9-Judg7:11\">JDG 7:9–7:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:2\">JDG 18:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:5-Judg18:10\">JDG 18:5–18:10</a></p>\n<h2>Avoiding warfare</h2>\n<h3>Making a treaty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:15\">JOS 9:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:28-Gen26:29\">GEN 26:28–26:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:1\">JOS 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:1\">1SA 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:12\">1KI 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Representative combat</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:8-1Sam17:10\">1SA 17:8–17:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:12-2Sam2:17\">2SA 2:12–2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Strategies employed in warfare</h2>\n<h3>Dividing into groups</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:43-Judg9:44\">JDG 9:43–9:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:14-Gen14:15\">GEN 14:14–14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:7-Gen32:8\">GEN 32:7–32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:16-Judg7:21\">JDG 7:16–7:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:11\">1SA 11:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:1-2Sam18:2\">2SA 18:1–18:2</a></p>\n<h3>Attacking by night</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:19\">JDG 7:19</a></strong> <em>The Hebrews divided the night into three watches.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:14-Gen14:15\">GEN 14:14–14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:36\">1SA 14:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:5\">JER 6:5</a></p>\n<h3>Setting an ambush</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr13:13-2Chr13:14\">2CH 13:13–13:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:4-Josh8:7\">JOS 8:4–8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:34\">JDG 9:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:42-Judg9:44\">JDG 9:42–9:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:29-Judg20:44\">JDG 20:29–20:44</a></p>\n<h3>Swiftness of action</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:19\">JOS 8:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:6-Josh10:9\">JOS 10:6–10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:7\">JOS 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:22-2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:22–5:25</a></p>\n<h2>Trusting in God in warfare</h2>\n<h3>Of greater importance than military might or prowess</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:1\">DEU 20:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7\">PSA 20:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:45-1Sam17:47\">1SA 17:45–17:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:16-Ps33:17\">PSA 33:16–33:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:10-Ps147:11\">PSA 147:10–147:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">ZEC 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>Demonstrated by seeking God before a battle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg1:1\">JDG 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:27-Judg20:28\">JDG 20:27–20:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:18-2Sam5:19\">2SA 5:18–5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:22-2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:22–5:25</a></p>\n<h3>Strengthened by seeing God fighting for Israel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:29-Exod14:31\">EXO 14:29–14:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:10-Josh10:14\">JOS 10:10–10:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:35\">2KI 19:35</a></p>",
